<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v10" title="Q30_v10" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Mariana y Paula compran una caja de galletas artesanales para vender en una feria escolar. El costo total de la caja es de $<m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>. Mariana aporta $<m:math><m:mn>5000</m:mn></m:math> y Paula aporta el resto del dinero.
    </p>
    <p>
      Venden todas las galletas y obtienen en total $<m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>. Quieren repartir ese dinero en proporción al aporte que hizo cada una. A continuación se muestran cuatro posibles montos que podría recibir Paula.
      
      ¿Cuál de los siguientes montos es coherente con un reparto proporcional al aporte de cada una?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">$<m:math><m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn></m:math><qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Paula aportó el resto de <m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, así que el reparto debe hacerse en razón <m:math><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces Paula debe recibir <m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>17&#160;500</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, este monto no es coherente con un reparto proporcional.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">$<m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math><qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Paula aportó <m:math><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> de un total de <m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> del total. Por eso debe recibir <m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, este monto no corresponde al reparto proporcional pedido.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">$<m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math><qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Paula aportó <m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces los aportes de Mariana y Paula están en razón <m:math><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>. Paula debe recibir <m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>. Por lo tanto, $<m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> es coherente con el reparto proporcional.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">$<m:math><m:mn>35&#160;000</m:mn></m:math><qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si el reparto es proporcional al aporte, Paula debe recibir la fracción <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> de <m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>. Ese cálculo da <m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>35&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, este monto no cumple la proporcionalidad del problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso: reparto proporcional según el aporte</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Determinar cuánto aportó Paula</strong></p>
            <p>El costo total de la caja es $<m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Mariana aporta $<m:math><m:mn>5000</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces Paula aporta el resto:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, Paula aportó $<m:math><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Escribir la razón entre los aportes</strong></p>
            <p>Mariana y Paula aportaron, respectivamente, $<m:math><m:mn>5000</m:mn></m:math> y $<m:math><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La razón es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Esto significa que el dinero obtenido debe repartirse en 4 partes iguales: 1 parte para Mariana y 3 partes para Paula.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Repartir los $40 000 según esa proporción</strong></p>
            <p>El total recaudado es $<m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Como la proporción total es <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> partes, cada parte vale:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Paula recibe 3 partes, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar con una fracción del total aportado</strong></p>
            <p>Paula aportó <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> del dinero inicial.</p>
            <p>Entonces debe recibir <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> de $<m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Se obtiene el mismo resultado.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El monto que puede recibir Paula en un reparto proporcional al aporte de cada una es $<m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>C</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>